<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{{> template/title }}</title>
</head>
<body>
{{> template/header}}
<section class="main-contents">
    <div class="main-top">
        <div class="main-text">
            <h2 class="text-title">여행을 쓰자,<br>
                <span class="text-yolo">욜로</span>
            </h2>
            <div class="text-msg">
                여행의 소중한 순간을 볼로에 담아보세요. <br>
                메모, 사진 경로, 위치를 간편하게 작성하면, <br>
                볼로가 멋진 여행기를 만들어 드립니다.
            </div>
            <img class="text-img" src="./img/harubang.png">
        </div>
        <div class="main-event">
            <img class="event-img" src="./img/banner-event.png">
        </div>
        <ul class="main-tag">
            <li style="background-image: url(./img/holo.jpg)">
                <div class="dark-layer">
                    #나홀로여행
                </div>
            </li>
            <li style="background-image: url(./img/eat.png)">
                <div class="dark-layer">
                    #먹방여행
                </div>
            </li>
            <li style="background-image: url(./img/banner-tip.png)">
                <div class="dark-layer">
                    욜로 사용법
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="main-mid">
    <ul>
        <li class="main-country">
            <div class="conti-name">Europe</div>
            <img class="country-img" src="./img/europe.png">
            <ul class="country">
                <li>스페인</li>
                <li>프랑스</li>
                <li>영국</li>
                <li>이태리</li>
                <li>독일</li>
                <li>포르투갈</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li class="main-country">
            <div class="conti-name">America&<br>Oceania</div>
            <img class="country-img" src="./img/america.png">
            <ul class="country">
                <li>미국</li>
                <li>캐나다</li>
                <li>호주</li>
                <li>뉴욕</li>
                <li>멕시코</li>
                <li>쿠바</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li class="main-country">
            <div class="conti-name">Asia</div>
            <img class="country-img" src="./img/asia.png">
            <ul class="country">
                <li>일본</li>
                <li>대만</li>
                <li>홍콩</li>
                <li>태국</li>
                <li>베트남</li>
                <li>싱가폴</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ul>
</section>
{{> template/footer}}
</body>
</html>
